data.description: Impressive 2 story gem in the exciting gated community of Canyon Gate is ready now. This home is perfect for those desiring a home ready for updates, minor work and repairs. A true value at $127/sf.. Cinco Ranch is known for their amenities and A+ Katy ISD schools. The home offers a large kitchen with tons of cabinets and counterspace. Washer, dryer, fridge are included. The family room offers big beautiful windows, a corner fireplace w nice views of the pool size backyard and patio areas. Primary bed and bath are  down and features a deep soaking jetted tub and an incredible walk in closet. This well laid out floorplan offers two large flex rooms downstairs and a large gameroom up. This home sits on a large gorgeous corner lot with an oversize 2 car garage that includes a workshop w a/c and has an extra long driveway for extra family and friends. Don't miss this amazing opportunity. Come see it today!
